{"metadata": {"team_id": "apparent", "run_id": "apparent-defendant", "topic_id": "1015"}, "responses": [{"text": "Flat Earth societies exist in UK universities: York, Nottingham Trent, Cambridge.", "citations": ["4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_669431569"]}, {"text": "The flat Earth hypothesis claims Earth is a disk surrounded by a 46\u2011meter ice wall.", "citations": ["4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_669431569"]}, {"text": "Richard Dawkins criticized UK universities for tolerating flat Earth beliefs.", "citations": ["4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_669431569"]}, {"text": "Ashraf Al\u2011Kaali, a Tunisian media personality, claims Earth is flat citing religious texts.", "citations": ["7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951"]}, {"text": "Al\u2011Kaali asserts scientific and philosophical evidence supports flat Earth.", "citations": ["7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951"]}, {"text": "Kamel El\u2011Rihawi criticized Al\u2011Kaali\u2019s flat\u2011Earth claim as regressive and harmful.", "citations": ["7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951"]}, {"text": "Flat\u2011Earth believers commented on Virgin Galactic livestream, claiming launch disproved curvature.", "citations": ["4a564c34-5ed1-4d7d-961c-125e44d9f0aa_999086473"]}, {"text": "They argue Earth is flat because launch did not show an oval shape.", "citations": ["4a564c34-5ed1-4d7d-961c-125e44d9f0aa_999086473"]}, {"text": "Several NFL players publicly claim Earth is flat, including Travis Kelce and Jason Kelce.", "citations": ["234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180"]}, {"text": "Dr. Rosenpenis proposed a donut\u2011shaped Earth model in 2008.", "citations": ["8766810f-1640-41f6-b68c-298343537279_1001418094"]}, {"text": "V. Varaug suggested a torus Earth model in 2012, claiming light bends around the hole.", "citations": ["8766810f-1640-41f6-b68c-298343537279_1001418094"]}, {"text": "Varaug argued the Earth\u2019s hole is invisible because light follows the torus curve.", "citations": ["8766810f-1640-41f6-b68c-298343537279_1001418094"]}, {"text": "Varaug claimed gravity pulls toward the donut\u2019s \u201cjam\u201d side, explaining day/night.", "citations": ["8766810f-1640-41f6-b68c-298343537279_1001418094"]}, {"text": "Scientists refuted the donut model: Sun would not rise/set correctly.", "citations": ["8766810f-1640-41f6-b68c-298343537279_1001418094"]}, {"text": "Flat earthers reject gravity, satellite imagery, and claim governments hide truth.", "citations": ["622d24ae-9987-4fda-a84c-bb94203f6c65_1060788103"]}, {"text": "The flat Earth movement is described as a \u201cgold rush\u201d of the era.", "citations": ["6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320"]}, {"text": "Resurgence linked to rebellion against modern science and a \u201cgold rush\u201d mentality.", "citations": ["6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320"]}, {"text": "Flat Earth argument rooted in long\u2011standing religious belief that Earth is flat.", "citations": ["6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320"]}, {"text": "Believers portrayed as leaving reality, dreaming nonsense, and seeking isolation.", "citations": ["6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320"]}, {"text": "Movement uses psychological suggestion to shape general knowledge and is influenced by mystical factors.", "citations": ["6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320"]}], "references": ["4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_669431569", "a6fb51a1-33fb-4c82-a04f-27da658e6240_503588335", "00310f0f-f13a-484e-a6fe-9e53d1ab632d_486305547", "6e47a5cf-47a7-42a3-812e-ef81ba1e7a5f_46222320", "8766810f-1640-41f6-b68c-298343537279_1001418094", "a82fde8a-9e03-4821-93dd-3732d46d41c4_975752910", "234c0ac8-224a-4ae9-b9fc-df4652c033eb_450387180", "7614d155-5beb-49f4-b13a-4f2675a1d6c8_866557951", "bb504df7-75f4-4d5f-a1c5-be1652e12594_703346419", "622d24ae-9987-4fda-a84c-bb94203f6c65_1060788103", "f0932c14-bf26-4a29-a8e3-cbacb4a1a279_599324161", "d05dbf8e-491a-48dd-a881-89a171e3d635_6659815